**Voluntary Retirement Scheme (VRS)** benefits typically include: ex-gratia payment (salary × months × service years), gratuity (up to ₹20L tax-free), leave encashment (up to 30 days per year tax-free), and EPF/NPS corpus. Government employees under VRS Rule 25 or 39 receive different formulas. This calculator covers the key components of VRS compensation.
